==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: qiĕ tīng xiàhuí fēnjiĕ

===Etymology===
A common phrase from the days of radio broadcasts

===Phrase===
'''[[且]][[听]][[下回]][[分解]]'''
# [said at the end of a radio-play broadcast] Tune in next time to hear the next installment of our story.

===Alternate forms===
[[且聽下回分解]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])
